The woman in this painting has jet black hair, snowy white pale skin and voluptuous red lips. Oddly her pupil less eyes seem to shift and follow you around.

A delicate vase holds vibrant, colorful flowers of purple and yellow, their scent hangs thick and salty in the air. Close inspection shows a glistening, thick red liquid that appears to seep from the stems and slowly run down into the dirt.
